# textdomain: mcl_tools
Pickaxes are mining tools to mine hard blocks, such as stone. A pickaxe can also be used as weapon, but it is rather inefficient.=Os picos son ferramentas de minería para extraer bloques duros, como a pedra. Un pico tambén se pode empregar como arma, pero e bastante ineficiente.
An axe is your tool of choice to cut down trees, wood-based blocks and other blocks. Axes deal a lot of damage as well, but they are rather slow.=Unha machada e a sua ferramenta de elección para cortar árbores, bloques a base de madeira e outros bloques. As machadas tambén causan moito dano, pero son bastante lentas.
Swords are great in melee combat, as they are fast, deal high damage and can endure countless battles. Swords can also be used to cut down a few particular blocks, such as cobwebs.=As espadas son excelentes no combate corpo a corpo, xa que son rápidas, inflixen moito dano e poden soportar innumerables batallas. As espadas tambén se poden usar para cortar alguns bloques en particular, como arañeiras.
To slash multiple enemies, hold the sword in your hand, then use (rightclick) an enemy.=
Shovels are tools for digging coarse blocks, such as dirt, sand and gravel. They can also be used to turn grass blocks to grass paths. Shovels can be used as weapons, but they are very weak.=As pas son ferramentas para cavar bloques grosos, como terra, area e grava. Tamén se poden usar para convertir bloques de herba en sendeiros de herba. As pas poden empregarse como armas, pero son moi febles.
To turn a grass block into a grass path, hold the shovel in your hand, then use (rightclick) the top or side of a grass block. This only works when there's air above the grass block.=Para convertir un bloque de herba nun camiño de herba, sosteña a pa coa man e despois faga (clic dereito) na parte superior ou lateral dun bloque de herba. Isto só funciona cando hai aire sobre o bloque de herba.
Shears are tools to shear sheep and to mine a few block types. Shears are a special mining tool and can be used to obtain the original item from grass, leaves and similar blocks that require cutting.=As tesoiras son ferramentas para esquilar ovellas e extraer alguns tipos de bloques. As tesoiras son unha ferramenta de minería especial e podense empegar para obter o artículo orixinal de herba, follas e bloques similares que requiren corte.
To shear sheep or carve faceless pumpkins, use the “place” key on them. Faces can only be carved at the side of faceless pumpkins. Mining works as usual, but the drops are different for a few blocks.=Para esquilar ovellas ou tallar cabazas sen rostro, use a tecla "colocar" nelas. As caras só se poden tallar a carón das cabazas sen rostro. A minería funciona como de costume, pero as gotas son diferentes para alguns bloques.
